lead_paragraph: Dylan Strome is living his NHL dream playing for the Arizona Coyotes, staying in a hotel and avoiding the harsh Pennsylvania winter he endured the past three years playing for the Ontario Hockey League's Erie Otters.

headline.print_headline: Nine-Game NHL Tryouts Create Uncertainty for Young Players
